entries.title: Talonbane Cobra: The Destruction
entries.title_d: 'The infamous Talonbane Cobra! Laetin was right. The heartless assassin knows how to fly! No matter. I will come out victorious and win the day! When I have defeated the Talonbane Cobra, I should return to Laetin with the good news.'
